headline: Mosaic Announces Closing of Share Purchase and Subscription Agreement with Ma'aden
summary: TAMPA, FL / ACCESSWIRE / January 2, 2025 / The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) announced that it has completed the transaction with Saudi Arabian Mining Company (Ma'aden) to sell the interest it holds in Ma'aden Wa'ad Al Shamal Phosphate Company (MWSPC) ...
